<lb n="0452a13" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 180</head>
<lb n="0452a14" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0452002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0452002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452002"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>過去<note n="0452003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世〕－【三】</note><note n="0452003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔世〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452003"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>佛分衛經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0452a15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0452a16" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0452004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔西晉…三藏〕七字－【宋】</note><app n="0452004" word-count="7"><lem wit="【大】">西晉<note n="0452005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔月氏國〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0452005"><lem wit="【大】">月氏國</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0452006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三藏＋（法師）【元】【明】</note><app n="0452006"><lem wit="【大】">三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">三藏法師</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0452a17" ed="T"/><div type="jing"><p id="pT03p0452a1701">佛言：「<note n="0452007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＋（去）【三】</note><note n="0452007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過＋（去）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452007"><lem wit="【大】">過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">過去</rdg></app>世有佛入城分衛，與尊弟子諸菩
<lb n="0452a18" ed="T"/>薩俱；弟子菩薩姿容相好，皆悉端正，如本所
<lb n="0452a19" ed="T"/>行各得其道。</p><p id="pT03p0452a1906" place="inline">「有一母人，&CB00775;<note n="0452008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身＝娠【元】【明】</note><app n="0452008"><lem wit="【大】">身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">娠</rdg></app>數月，見佛及
<lb n="0452a20" ed="T"/>僧有所至<note n="0452009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奏＝湊【三】</note><note n="0452009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奏＝湊【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452009"><lem wit="【大】">奏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">湊</rdg></app>，心自計願：『我所懷子生，如此
<lb n="0452a21" ed="T"/>使為沙門佛弟子。』日月滿足即生安隱，兒亦
<lb n="0452a22" ed="T"/>姝好與眾人異，母以恩愛無<note n="0452010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝厭【三】</note><note n="0452010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意＝厭【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452010"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">厭</rdg></app>令兒行作沙
<lb n="0452a23" ed="T"/>門，中有覺意，即自念言：『我前有願，若我生
<lb n="0452a24" ed="T"/>子當使為道，兒今已生，有異凡人，令我安隱，
<lb n="0452a25" ed="T"/>復無惡露，不可戀<note n="0452011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嫪＝&CB00387;【三】</note><note n="0452011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嫪＝&CB00387;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452011"><lem wit="【大】">嫪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB00387;</rdg></app>恩愛之故，違我本心。』</p>
<lb n="0452a26" ed="T"/><p id="pT03p0452a2601">「子年七歲，家復貧狹，即作二人飯具，及三法
<lb n="0452a27" ed="T"/>衣，手持澡瓶，自將其子行詣佛所，稽首佛足，
<lb n="0452a28" ed="T"/>前白佛言：『願哀我子使為沙門，令後得道，身
<lb n="0452a29" ed="T"/>形如佛。』佛即聽之，令作沙門。母以澡<note n="0452012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">灌＝罐【三】</note><note n="0452012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">灌＝罐【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452012"><lem wit="【大】">灌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">罐</rdg></app>，前<pb n="0452b" ed="T" id="T03.0180.0452b"/>
<lb n="0452b01" ed="T"/><note n="0452013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洗＝酒【宋】</note><app n="0452013"><lem wit="【大】">洗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">酒</rdg></app>兒手，應時九龍從瓶口出，吐水灌兒手
<lb n="0452b02" ed="T"/>中，澡訖殘水散兒頭上，水之潺<note n="0452014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">渧＝滴【三】</note><note n="0452014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">渧＝滴【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452014"><lem wit="【大】">渧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">滴</rdg></app>於兒頭
<lb n="0452b03" ed="T"/>上，化成華蓋珠交絡帳。中有師子座，上有坐
<lb n="0452b04" ed="T"/>佛。佛笑，口中五色光出，照十億佛剎，還遶佛
<lb n="0452b05" ed="T"/>身從兒頂入。母以飯具前上佛，并食其<note n="0452015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＋（子）【三】</note><note n="0452015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子＋（子）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452015"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">子子</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0452b06" ed="T"/>便發無上平等道意，應時十億佛剎為六<note n="0452016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝返【三】</note><note n="0452016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">反＝返【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452016"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">返</rdg></app>
<lb n="0452b07" ed="T"/>震動，眾剎諸佛皆自然現。佛以母飯飽，爾
<lb n="0452b08" ed="T"/>所佛及諸比丘僧皆等飽足，其飯如故，亦不
<lb n="0452b09" ed="T"/>損減；母即歡喜，及無數天人皆得阿惟越致。</p>
<lb n="0452b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT03p0452b1001">「時，兒髮墮成為沙門，即亦得立不退轉地。母
<lb n="0452b11" ed="T"/>前白佛：『今我所見，有三可怪：我澡兒手九龍
<lb n="0452b12" ed="T"/>吐水，此一可怪；澡已殘水散兒頭上，化成寶
<lb n="0452b13" ed="T"/>帳，及師子座上有坐佛，是二可怪；佛笑口
<lb n="0452b14" ed="T"/>中光從兒頂入，是三可怪；願佛為我分別說
<lb n="0452b15" ed="T"/>之。』佛言：『此兒<note n="0452017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00230;＝起【宋】，印【元】</note><note n="0452017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00230;＝起【宋】，＝印【元】</note><app n="0452017"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00230;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">起</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">印</rdg></app>後十四劫當得作佛，九龍
<lb n="0452b16" ed="T"/>當浴，師子座華蓋寶帳，佛笑光從兒頂入，皆
<lb n="0452b17" ed="T"/>是其應。』母聞佛言倍懷踊躍，後<note n="0452018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＋（得）【三】</note><note n="0452018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＋（得）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452018"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">當得</rdg></app>作母人
<lb n="0452b18" ed="T"/>轉輪聖王，積七百世竟，其劫壽盡轉母人身，
<lb n="0452b19" ed="T"/>當得阿惟越致。」</p><p id="pT03p0452b1907" place="inline">佛言：「是時小兒，我身是；我
<lb n="0452b20" ed="T"/>今於世功德如是。」諸天龍神、一切人民，聞佛
<lb n="0452b21" ed="T"/>所說，皆得阿惟越致。</p>
<lb n="0452b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT03p0452b2201">　無熱佛　性空佛　天王佛　金仁佛</p>
<lb n="0452b23" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><note n="0452019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0452019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452019"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>過去<note n="0452020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世〕－【三】</note><note n="0452020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔世〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452020"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>佛分衛經</jhead></juan></div>
</body></text></TEI.2>
